314
00:26:47,706 --> 00:26:49,105
Do you remember me?

315
00:26:49,374 --> 00:26:51,274
Yes, I do.

316
00:26:51,443 --> 00:26:54,276
Your friend gave me your phone number.

317
00:26:55,947 --> 00:26:58,780
