318
00:26:59,751 --> 00:27:04,085
I've a friend
who works at the audio company.

319
00:27:05,357 --> 00:27:07,018
Tap...

320
00:27:07,092 --> 00:27:11,586
Will, why are you called Tap?

321
00:27:12,097 --> 00:27:17,763
My name is Stephenie,
