324
00:27:25,543 --> 00:27:26,271
And you?

325
00:27:26,645 --> 00:27:30,046
I'm a F.7 student in St. Marynold.

326
00:27:30,348 --> 00:27:32,248
A famous school.

327
00:27:33,518 --> 00:27:34,678
What about you?

328
00:27:34,719 --> 00:27:36,619
I'm also a F.7 student.

329
00:27:36,788 --> 00:27:37,948
Which school?

330
00:27:38,189 --> 00:27:40,350
La Salle.

331
00:27:40,592 --> 00:27:44,153
OK... why don't we exchange
our school prospectus?

332
00:27:44,996 --> 00:27:48,159
Sure, how?

333
00:27:49,868 --> 00:27:51,096
You decide.

334
00:27:51,670 --> 00:27:53,661
Let's meet this Sunday afternoon.

335
00:27:53,805 --> 00:27:55,363
OK, it's a deal, bye.

336
00:28:03,481 --> 00:28:05,642
- Hello?
- Hello?

337
00:28:05,684 --> 00:28:07,151
