349
00:29:43,581 --> 00:29:45,481
What's going on?

350
00:29:51,656 --> 00:29:54,056
Mentor, if you manage to eat
this last bowl,

351
00:29:54,092 --> 00:29:56,060
You'll win the super prize.

352
00:29:56,161 --> 00:29:57,389
