361
00:30:19,551 --> 00:30:21,883
Yeah!

362
00:30:26,191 --> 00:30:28,022
Yeah!

363
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:32,729
Congratulations,
you've won our super prize, you get $750

364
00:30:32,831 --> 00:30:35,163
