385
00:31:25,984 --> 00:31:29,977
You're so tall.

386
00:31:30,221 --> 00:31:31,552
Don't be like this.

387
00:31:31,823 --> 00:31:32,551
Am I?

388
00:31:32,857 --> 00:31:34,017
