395
00:31:53,711 --> 00:31:55,542
It's OK...

396
00:31:56,481 --> 00:31:59,211
You're really very tall.

397
00:32:13,598 --> 00:32:15,429
Miss, please.

398
00:32:15,566 --> 00:32:16,965
Thanks.

399
00:32:21,673 --> 00:32:22,970
