I've forgotten to bring mine.

404
00:32:43,227 --> 00:32:45,058
I'll bring it the next time.

405
00:32:46,297 --> 00:32:48,288
It's alright.

406
00:32:49,734 --> 00:32:53,226
Composition champion, javelin champion.

407
00:32:53,271 --> 00:32:56,263
