411
00:33:07,552 --> 00:33:09,281
Football Club.

412
00:33:09,454 --> 00:33:12,355
Football Club? Football Team?

413
00:33:12,657 --> 00:33:14,147
Yeah.

414
00:33:14,492 --> 00:33:16,983
La Salle Football team?

415
00:33:17,095 --> 00:33:20,155
Do you know Johnny and Stephen?

416
00:33:20,431 --> 00:33:24,424
I... played football with them
