418
00:33:30,575 --> 00:33:32,907
Johnny?

419
00:33:33,344 --> 00:33:35,244
Johnny Koo.

420
00:33:35,413 --> 00:33:38,314
Not him, I mean Johnny Chan.

421
00:33:38,483 --> 00:33:42,476
