422
00:33:42,653 --> 00:33:44,712
We keep in touch with each other.

423
00:33:57,769 --> 00:34:00,101
Do you have time, later on?

424
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,231
...why don't we meet another day.

425
00:34:04,409 --> 00:34:05,967
