436
00:35:00,498 --> 00:35:03,228
But luckily you've got me as friend.

437
00:35:03,334 --> 00:35:05,165
OK, just count on me.

438
00:35:05,369 --> 00:35:07,098
Hello? Aunt, Angie speaking.

439
00:35:07,271 --> 00:35:09,432
Tap will be at my house tonight
for a project,

440
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:12,200
