456
00:37:10,628 --> 00:37:12,789
Let me see you home by taxi.

457
00:37:13,431 --> 00:37:15,331
Let's take a bus.

458
00:37:15,433 --> 00:37:18,266
Then we can spend more time together.

459
00:37:51,035 --> 00:37:53,367
Bye-bye.

460
00:38:02,813 --> 00:38:05,714
OK, let's count three, and then...

461
00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:08,182
Let's part after saying good-bye.

462
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:11,920
One, two...

463
00:38:22,233 --> 00:38:24,724
I must go home.

464
00:38:27,772 --> 00:38:28,670
One.

465
00:38:29,573 --> 00:38:30,631
Two.

466
00:38:31,042 --> 00:38:32,441
Three.

467
00:38:32,777 --> 00:38:34,005
Bye-bye.

468
00:38:57,635 --> 00:38:58,795
