492
00:40:51,749 --> 00:40:53,410
Hello, come and sit here.

493
00:40:53,484 --> 00:40:54,815
Mom.

494
00:40:57,822 --> 00:40:58,880
Hong.

495
00:40:59,123 --> 00:41:00,852
